(43, 6, 67, 42, 14, 25, 33, 'Will ye also go away?', 'Discipleship and Commitment', 'Both passages emphasize the cost of discipleship. In John 6:67, Jesus questions the twelve about their commitment, while Luke 14:25-33 outlines the sacrifices required to follow Him.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini')
